#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Visual Dictionary"
msgstr "Un dictionnaire visuel"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasma-workspaces; feature many different graphical user interface "
"elements, commonly known as <quote>widgets</quote>. This guide will "
"introduce you to their names and functions."
msgstr ""
"Les &plasma-workspaces; fournissent beaucoup d'éléments graphiques de "
"l'interface utilisateur différents, communément appelés <quote>composants "
"graphiques</quote>. Ce guide vous mènera à leurs noms et fonctions."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Big Picture"
msgstr "Généralités"

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Les fenêtres"

